## Quality Gates

```bash
# These must all pass before any commit:
./vendor/bin/pint --test                              # Code style
./vendor/bin/phpstan analyse --memory-limit=512M      # Static analysis (level 8+)
php artisan test --parallel --coverage --min=100       # Tests + 100% coverage
```

## What NOT To Do

- Do NOT create Repository classes. Use Eloquent directly or Action classes.
- Do NOT create Service classes that just proxy model methods.
- Do NOT create Interfaces for classes with only one implementation.
- Do NOT use `env()` outside of `config/` files.
- Do NOT lazy load relationships. Use `preventLazyLoading()`.
- Do NOT catch exceptions just to log and re-throw.
